column11:
  This paper shows $$ \sup_{f\in H^s(\mathbb{R}^n)}\dim
_H\left\{x\in\mathbb{R}^n:\ \lim_{t\rightarrow0}e^{it(-\Delta)^\alpha}f(x)\neq
f(x)\right\}\leq n+1-\frac{2(n+1)s}{n}\ \ \text{under}\ \ \begin{cases}
n\geq2;\\ \alpha>\frac12;
  \frac{n}{2(n+1)}<s\leq\frac{n}{2} . \end{cases} $$
